  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Blitz Arena is a competitive and dynamic PARTY GAME shooter. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play a tournament with 8 players in a multitude of game modes to emerge victorious. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Alone or in a team, prepare yourself for versus, battle royale, dodgeball, gun games and several other game modes... </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You will have to finish as high as possible to earn points on each mode to win the game.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>// Features //</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >15 Gamemodes</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >8 Maps</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >25 Weapons</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >9 Free unlockable skin</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Leaderboard</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Up to 8 players</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >10 grenades</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>// Gamemodes //</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Tournament 1v1</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2727490/extras/a03258b6f0fc3c0cbcab095398bacd96.poster.avif?t=1763213001\" width=800 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2727490/extras/a03258b6f0fc3c0cbcab095398bacd96.webm?t=1763213001\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2727490/extras/a03258b6f0fc3c0cbcab095398bacd96.mp4?t=1763213001\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong> </strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >All players compete in a 1v1 tournament table (Upper and loser bracket). The objective is to finish as high as possible in the tournament to collect points.   </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Gungame</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2727490/extras/c9b2422fdde4483420d5cafc3e12c6b7.poster.avif?t=1763213001\" width=800 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2727490/extras/c9b2422fdde4483420d5cafc3e12c6b7.webm?t=1763213001\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2727490/extras/c9b2422fdde4483420d5cafc3e12c6b7.mp4?t=1763213001\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>  </strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Do kills to level up and change weapons, the first team to complete all levels wins the game. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Dodge ball</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2727490/extras/de0b1786f050d6efbc0e6760d1051c65.poster.avif?t=1763213001\" width=800 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2727490/extras/de0b1786f050d6efbc0e6760d1051c65.webm?t=1763213001\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2727490/extras/de0b1786f050d6efbc0e6760d1051c65.mp4?t=1763213001\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play ping-pong with remote-controlled rockets, throw rocket on your enemies with your gun! Be careful, the rocket speeds up with each dodge!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Elimination confirmé</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2727490/extras/3edf43289885c2a7840db2fb7813806e.poster.avif?t=1763213001\" width=800 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2727490/extras/3edf43289885c2a7840db2fb7813806e.webm?t=1763213001\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2727490/extras/3edf43289885c2a7840db2fb7813806e.mp4?t=1763213001\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Do kills and collect enemy soul, the first team to reach 30 enemy souls collected wins the game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong> Battle Royal</strong>  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2727490/extras/de686dccc19de157f71d552c6060f642.poster.avif?t=1763213001\" width=800 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2727490/extras/de686dccc19de157f71d552c6060f642.webm?t=1763213001\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2727490/extras/de686dccc19de157f71d552c6060f642.mp4?t=1763213001\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Jump out of the plane, find loots, prepare yourself for the final fight but be careful, the area moves very quickly!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <br><strong>Aim target</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2727490/extras/4b2c8046be0b26a24aad7bf2146600a1.poster.avif?t=1763213001\" width=800 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2727490/extras/4b2c8046be0b26a24aad7bf2146600a1.webm?t=1763213001\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2727490/extras/4b2c8046be0b26a24aad7bf2146600a1.mp4?t=1763213001\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Over 3 rounds with different speeds, shoot as many targets as possible to earn points.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Runner</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2727490/extras/0f4e039ac3e097d65d17732ace07c76a.poster.avif?t=1763213001\" width=800 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2727490/extras/0f4e039ac3e097d65d17732ace07c76a.webm?t=1763213001\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2727490/extras/0f4e039ac3e097d65d17732ace07c76a.mp4?t=1763213001\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Complete the parcours as quickly as possible while shooting at the targets. Don't miss one, otherwise a penalty will be given to you!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>And much more to discover...</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2727490/extras/b1e9c84db6d328ad36eae57d80dfa1e7.poster.avif?t=1763213001\" width=800 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2727490/extras/b1e9c84db6d328ad36eae57d80dfa1e7.webm?t=1763213001\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2727490/extras/b1e9c84db6d328ad36eae57d80dfa1e7.mp4?t=1763213001\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
